The 2023 Asus ROG Zephyrus G14 is widely available everywhere at the time of this review (late Aug 2023).

The top-tier ROG Zephyrus G14 GA402XY model reviewed here, with the Ryzen 9 7940HS, RTX 4090 Laptop dGPU, 32 GB of RAM, 1 TB of SSD storage, and the mini LED display, is listed at 2999 USD in the US, around 3999 EUR here in Europe and 3299 GBP in the UK.

Lower specced models are available as well. The best-value configuration is the Ryzen 9 + RTX 4060 + QHD IPS panel, available for $1599 in the US, and 1899 EUR here in Europe. Just keep in mind that this one comes with 8 GB onboard + 8 GB DIMM of memory.

